headline: 3 No-Brainer High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy With $100 Right Now
summary: Toronto-Dominion Bank is out of favor but its troubles are manageable.  Realty Income is a slow and steady tortoise but its yield makes up for that.  Alexandria Real Estate is hyper focused but its dividend is well covered and a turnaround seems likely.
